{"tid":2153473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警發信指蘋果如果下星期一無收到法律文件  警方即可查閱所有新聞材料","createTime":"2020-08-12T14:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T15:20:24.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e757d9e8ad9f250b244861eb5e6b4e1e5bff77aa","tid":2153473,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"警方周一搜捕壹傳媒高層，派近三百警力佔領《蘋果》大樓撿走大量文件後，警務處處長向《蘋果》發信開出7天限期通牒，限《蘋果》在下星期一前採取法律行動，以保護涉及保密權的資料，否則警方將會解封文件查閱。證物列表披露，警方在《蘋果》編採工作心臟地帶至少取走兩叠放在書桌上的文件，若文件涉新聞材料，警方勢違反法庭手令。日前要求監察警方搜證卻被警員推撞的總編輯羅偉光，據悉將向法庭呈交誓章，表明警方撿取了新聞材料，要求頒令禁止警方查看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/HJMXAKEPV4C6VHGT6547QBMTMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FHJMXAKEPV4C6VHGT6547QBMTMU%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=313ce902\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FHJMXAKEPV4C6VHGT6547QBMTMU%2F&h=e2126f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/HJMXAKEPV4C6VHGT6547QBMTMU/</a>"},{"pid":"58e1a8d1b77fe316068085dc36b78f9f2295a05d","tid":2153473,"uid":194298,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"我就唔撚信未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374eca53872c0e6203ad4bf809f9877584ecda39","tid":2153473,"uid":300644,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"扮咩嘢，肯定已經睇緊"},{"pid":"690ef4630e1f19c027e126ab34f2310297ce0b4b","tid":2153473,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=